OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMist and fog clearing, though
OL,6,Flow cloud locally lingering along
OL,7,Fsouthern coasts during Wednesday.
OL,8,FOtherwise, a dry day with an
OL,9,Fincreasing amount of pleasant spring
OL,10,Fsunshine developing. Feeling mild with
OL,11,Fjust a slight breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying dry this evening and
OL,14,Fovernight with prolonged clear spells
OL,15,Ffor most. Patchy mist and fog
OL,16,Freforming, though more isolated than
OL,17,Fthe previous night. Strengthening
OL,18,Fbreeze around the Moors.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
